Class ProxySnifferVarExtractorFormTarget

  • java.lang.Object

      • dfischer.proxysniffer.ProxySnifferVarExtractorFormTarget

  • public class ProxySnifferVarExtractorFormTarget
extends ProxySnifferVarExtractorDataInstance
    Extract the value for a var from a CGI parameter of a target-URL of a HTML form.
